data.meta_description:
23K likes, 139 comments - pleasedontquiz on June 11, 2024: "25 years ago on June 11, 1999 Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me was released in theaters. The film stars Mike Myers, Heather Graham, Seth Green, Verne Troyer, Rob Lowe, Robert Wagner, Mindy Sterling, Elizabeth Hurley, Will Ferrell and d Kristen Johnston. It was the third highest grossing film of the year, behind Star Wars: The Phantom Menace and The Sixth Sense. A sequel to 1997’s International Man of Mystery, the film was followed by 2002’s Goldmember.
